{
  "stem": "17821.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 122.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The Martinique is still considered as a province of France.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So what am I going to do about my husband?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, well, a couple of things happened.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I happened to know-- and I've forgotten the girls name-- terrible that I've forgotten it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I met a girl once in Paris, just met her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I happened to be with somebody and we met this young woman.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was introduced and there wasn't even much conversation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I just, just met this girl.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But somehow, by one of the miracles, she was in-- with the French government, in one of the government offices in-- oh, where was it-- where the French government was set up.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I typed up a letter saying, that this Martin Kessler needed to go to the, to, to the Martinique on business, which was really ridiculous.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Nobody was doing business in February 1940, '41.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But it looked OK on paper.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the manager of the Metro-Goldwyn-Mayer of Marseilles was nice enough to sign it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I sent that to Vichy because I had heard somehow that this girl was in a certain office in Vichy until she received it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so to say, I think she even said that, at some point, put on her hat and walked across to the, to the, to the what ministry-- what ministry, and asked someone to, oh, just put a stamp on this for me.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they put the stamp on it and she sent it back.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he had a permit to go on business to Martinique.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But how was he going to go?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now my boss, the top boss at Metro-Goldwyn owned, owned the horse farm in Normandy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Suddenly he turned up in Marseille.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was in New York, but he flew over.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
